{"tid":531751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啲靚女同醜女一齊玩會唔會有優越感？","createTime":"2018-01-17T07:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T10:18:13.000Z","uid":73112,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6412a7a2a45b24a6594ca9bbaf4bc6b37aec3905","tid":531751,"uid":73112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:12:49.000Z","msg":"當兩類人都係同一個生活圈子<br />\n大家係咁放相Tag大家做好姊妹咁樣<br />\n其實圈子內比較靚個啲會唔會有優越感？<br />\n會唔會自覺比啲醜女高一等？<br />\n會唔會成日利用醜女係到令自己更出眾？<br />\n會唔會產生某啲諗法？<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n「哎呀我咁靚都肯同咁醜樣嘅佢一齊玩我真係好人呀嘻嘻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n絲打巴打們有無意見可以分享下？<br />\n<br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8633a1858df0cb07bafc61349bfdf111ea6428a9","tid":531751,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"328c70f5cfd285d2e78d9a33b03b4b4e6d282a8a","tid":531751,"uid":73112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會，所以我專揀啲醜撚樣八婆同我做朋友，扮晒好姊妹噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同佢地相處係咪好有優越感，覺得自己整體好過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"94fae55b1ad32d930b5ea12d52c5a9df8593c537","tid":531751,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d922877c3b4797abae5a569744dbae174114aaf","tid":531751,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"有D人會, 有D人唔會<br />\n咁答好廢但現實就係咁"},{"pid":"7b6c1351d36121c1973f9affe8ce21af7368c986","tid":531751,"uid":10269,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"94fae55b1ad32d930b5ea12d52c5a9df8593c537","tid":531751,"uid":21423,"like":2,"disl